ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 27th day of August, 2008, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED and the Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus is DENIED.
Justice GREENSPAN did not participate in the consideration or decision of this matter.
